-- Merck KGaA CEO Sees Chemical Industry Growth Slowing in 2011, FTD Reports
-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 2010-10-20T05:09:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/merck-kgaa-ceo-sees-chemical-industry-growth-slowing-in-2011-ftd-reports.html
Merck KGaA Chief Executive Officer
Karl-Ludwig Kley expects growth in the chemicals industry to
slow next year as demand in China fails to compensate for slower
growth rates in industrialized nations, Financial Times
Deutschland reported from an event in Stuttgart, Germany.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  